# url()

**Instance Method**

Returns the URL used to initialize the receiver.

## Declaration

```swift
func url() -> URL?
```

## Return Value

The [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSURL] object used to initialize the receiver. This value can be `nil`.
